# TumbleBuff

**Tumblebuff**&nbsp;is a glitch which allows the player to buff weapons which you normally can't buff with sorceries, miracles or resins.

## External resources

- Tutorial with spells / miracles [https://youtu.be/gHa69W9Yjlc](https://youtu.be/gHa69W9Yjlc) by Delyssiya on YouTube.  This was found by [Eloise](https://www.youtube.com/@eloelo__) in january 2025.
- Demonstration with resin [https://youtu.be/mqL02DBS1UA](https://youtu.be/mqL02DBS1UA) by eloise on YouTube.
